[SPEAKER_00] ništa loše,

699
01:07:00,099 --> 01:07:01,860
[SPEAKER_00] to je isto jedan bit blagoslova

700
01:07:01,860 --> 01:07:03,239
[SPEAKER_00] i nije problem u novcu,

701
01:07:03,239 --> 01:07:04,639
