702
01:07:04,639 --> 01:07:05,460
[SPEAKER_00] prema tom novcu.

703
01:07:06,019 --> 01:07:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] Kad vidiš ljude koji imaju taj novac,

704
01:07:07,619 --> 01:07:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] a zadržali su skromnost,

705
01:07:08,960 --> 01:07:10,639
[SPEAKER_00] zadržali su jedan zdrav pogled

706
01:07:10,639 --> 01:07:11,260
[SPEAKER_00] prema tome,

707
01:07:11,260 --> 01:07:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] da onda mogu možda i pomoći

708
01:07:12,599 --> 01:07:13,519
[SPEAKER_00] drugima oko sebe,

709
01:07:13,519 --> 01:07:15,460
[SPEAKER_00] vidiš da je to jedna dimenzija

710
01:07:15,460 --> 01:07:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] koja,

711
01:07:15,960 --> 01:07:18,179
[SPEAKER_00] neću reći da je Alparis,

712
01:07:18,179 --> 01:07:19,400
[SPEAKER_00] a ovime već jednostavno

713
01:07:19,400 --> 01:07:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] svi ti prikazi svijeta

714
